------------------------------
PhpCaptcha Module
------------------------------

Provides a FormField which allows forms to validate for non-bot submissions
by giving them a challenge to decrypt an image or sound using the
Visual and Audio PHP CAPTCHA Generation Class by Ed Eliot from

http://www.ejeliot.com/pages/2

This module is also suplied with Bitstream Vers fonts from

http://www.gnome.org/fonts/

AUTHOR
------
Adam Walczak
Email: me@adamwalczak.info
WWW: www.adamwalczak.info

Polish SS community site:
www.silverstripe.org.pl

REQUIREMENTS
------------
At least SilverStripe 2.3 and the Spam Protection module

DOCUMENTATION
-------------
http://doc.silverstripe.com/doku.php?id=modules:phpcaptcha

INSTALL
-------

1) Copy the modules:phpcaptcha directory into your main SilverStripe directory
2) run ?flush=1